text: Pulane Motloung (born 3 October 1985 ) is a women's rugby union player from Jongalanga, Eastern Cape, South Africa. She played for Blue Bulls and the South Africa women's national rugby union team http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/rugby_union/welsh/8891699.stm == Career == She played in the 2010 Women's Rugby World Cup http://www.scrumqueens.com/news/sa- name-24-player-nations-cup-squad == References == ==External links== * http://www.sarugby.co.za/article.aspx?id=420549 Category:Living people Category:1985 births Category:South Africa national rugby union team captains Category:Blue Bulls players Category:Women of African descent Category:South African female rugby union players Category:Rugby union flankers
